Store current iptables rules to file a.

<pre>
sudo iptables-save > a
</pre>

Refactor the code.

{{Reload Firewall}}

Store current iptables rules to file b.

<pre>
sudo iptables-save > b
</pre>

Compare files a and b.

<pre>
diff a b
</pre>

There should be no diff.

